{"tid":1966282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾志將推逾百萬個「自救口罩」成本價售予黃店推動黃圈","createTime":"2020-04-10T05:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:12:20.000Z","uid":125168,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11eb31c445cfa6bbae5acb289dee98aa5d2531b1","tid":1966282,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，香港眾志繼於 2 月採購 130 萬個口罩發售後，今日（10日）宣布搜購了逾 100 萬個口罩，首批 35 萬個會以成本價每盒 100 元售予合作的黃店，推動港人支持黃色經濟圈，目前已與「渣哥」、「桔梗」等餐廳合作，亦歡迎其他黃店加入。這批口罩盒上亦印有「35 THX」字樣，代表立法會過半，以鼓勵港人盡快登記做選民 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%BE%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%80%8B-%E8%87%AA%E6%95%91%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E5%83%B9%E5%94%AE%E4%BA%88%E9%BB%83%E5%BA%97%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%88-%E5%B0%87%E8%88%87%E6%B8%A3%E5%93%A5-%E6%A1%94%E6%A2%97%E7%AD%89%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%2588-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B8%25A3%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E6%25A1%2594%25E6%25A2%2597%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%2F&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi68TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=22d57ad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2580%25BE%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2580%258B-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2594%25AE%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BA%2597%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258B%2595%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%2588-%25E5%25B0%